PrecisAuthority for the Minister of AGRICULTURE to enter into an AGREEMENT with the DISTRICT OF NORTH SAANICH which will permit the Department of Agriculture to install a sewer connection and to discharge sewage effluent from its Saanichton Plant Quarantine Station into the Bazan Bay Sewage Treatment Plant for a term of twenty (20) years.
